saadadb.query.parser
Class SelectFromIn

java.lang.Object
  saadadb.query.parser.SelectFromIn

public class SelectFromIn
extends java.lang.Object

This class parse the SaadaQL clause: SELECT category FROM * | class1 [, ...] IN * | coll [, ...] It stores the category, a list of class and a list of collection

Author:
F.X. Pineau
